name: OS 8.6
description:
A plus for McIntosh


This vaporwave work was done and rendered with blender cycles. It still focuses Macintosh advertising from the 80s that still amazes me. This time it focuses on the style of keyboards and the fonts they used. Also, the Macintosh is totally free in space. Only the light is animated but nothing else.

Also, Mac OS 8.6 was the System I played and designed everything on, but that was on a Power PC.
